svg.title: Plan A is the narrator’s sketch of the Vicarage and its walled garden, shown at the left end of a lane, above which is Miss Marple’s house, so neighboring the Vicarage to the right. A path opposite Miss Marple’s runs down towards the Old Hall with woods to the left. A studio is in the lower right corner of the Vicarage garden, visible from Miss Marple’s gate on the lane.
